name: Visible Thoughts: 010
description:
010 of the Visible Thoughts series.

I can't believe everyone likes these journal pages so much that I've made 10 of them already! I'm not sure how many more of them I'll make, but I know this isn't the end of them. I appreciate that my thoughts and the aesthetics of them are valued. If you've been sticking around and collecting them all -- thank you <3
